The '''Hutt underground''' or '''Hutt resistance''' was a [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] resistance movement formed during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]] by [[26 ABY/Legends|26 ABY]]. After the [[Battle of Nal Hutta]], they fought to free [[Hutt Space/Legends|Hutt Space]] of the invaders led by [[Nas Choka]]. [[Booster Terrik]], [[Captain/Legends|captain]] of the [[Imperial II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Imperial II''-class Star Destroyer]] ''[[Errant Venture/Legends|Errant Venture]]'', supplied them with weapons, although he charged them enough to make it profitable.

Later, after [[Bana Besadii Diori]] the Hutt was sent to negotiate with [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo]] at [[Shelter]] station, the [[Great River]] made inroads into helping the Hutts acquire non-weapon technology, such as medicine and food. One branch of the underground, the [[Sisar Runners]], was headed by [[Embra]].

